# Atomic oxygen electronic states (ground 3P and low-lying 1D, 1S), from
# NIST energy levels, with a uniform relaxation probability and a single
# spin class so every transition is allowed. Atomic O has no rotational or
# vibrational modes, so this deck exercises electronic relaxation driven
# purely by atom-atom collisions.
#     3P            1D               1S
O 3   0.0 0.5 5 1 0   22830.0 0.5 1 1 0   48621.0 0.5 5 1 0
